    "en": {
      "title": "There is no electricity for one hundred minutes at night and eighty minutes during the day",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Janaka Ratnayake, chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, said today (22nd) afternoon that due to lack of sufficient fuel and water for electricity generation, power cut was allowed for 3 hours tomorrow (23rd).",
        "Accordingly, Mr. Ratnayake said that electricity will be cut for 20 zones from 'A' to 'W' for 1 hour and 40 minutes during the day and 1 hour and 20 minutes at night."
      ],
